    "Due to the budget constraints, we use randomly sampled test set from both GENIA and BC5CDR for all experiments.",
    "We randomly sample 500 and 100 documents from GENIA and BC5CDR, respectively.",
    "Then, to verify each entity, we reconstruct context documents into entity-level input context.",
    "Specifically, we divide document per entity and verify each.",
    "We provide the detailed dataset statistics in Table 6, and detailed error ratio of the models in 7."
